{"title":"鄱阳湖呵！（诗二首）","authors":["王一民"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":9,"day":20}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄱阳湖呵！（诗二首）\t王一民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿绿的湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄橙橙的岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲤鱼肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄱阳湖呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的鱼米之乡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"公社派来远征队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄱阳湖边搭篷帐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开沟渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑堤圩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挡住滔滔洪浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拖拉机翻开黑土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"埋葬了千年的荒凉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汗水拌谷种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播下壮丽的诗行——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里湖岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里金光……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碧绿绿的湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄橙橙的岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三月收鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七月收粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鄱阳湖呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的鱼米之乡！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百里堤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了保护湖田洲地不受侵害，人们在鄱阳湖西岸筑一道百里长堤挡住了洪水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宽一道堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵绵长百里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宛如一把剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斩断鄱湖水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤外走渔船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤内种稻米；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋风阵阵吹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚禾正吐穗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二个公社派来巡逻队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日日夜夜守湖堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同在堤边宿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同饮湖中水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼是阴晴计，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炯炯察风雷；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心是百叶箱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包藏天与地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少风雨夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚滚山洪急，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水涨一尺高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堤高一丈几。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共一个太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一个意志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十二个公社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧扭在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宽宽一道堤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绵绵长百里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一道铜墙铁壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个坚强的集体。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}